### PlazaCMS Admin API Testing

### Health Check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787

### Login (create this user in your database first)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@plazacms.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get current user info
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get all attributes
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Create new attribute
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Color",
  "values": ["Red", "Blue", "Green", "Black", "White"]
}

### Create another attribute
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Size",
  "values": ["XS", "S", "M", "L", "XL", "XXL"]
}

### Get specific attribute
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes/ATTRIBUTE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update attribute name
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes/ATTRIBUTE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Updated Color"
}

### Add value to attribute
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes/ATTRIBUTE_ID_HERE/values
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "value": "Purple"
}

### Delete attribute value
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes/ATTRIBUTE_ID_HERE/values/VALUE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Delete attribute
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/admin/attributes/ATTRIBUTE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Logout
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/auth/logout
